snippet.title: Dreamstate | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dreamstate, can you survive your worst nightmare? In a point-and-click sit-and-survival psychological horror game, you fight off your nightmares throughout multiple nights to make it to the end of the week, with each night getting more challenging.

Where to get it: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3231460/Dreamstate/
Voice actors in the trailer:
https://www.voices.com/profile/saralemeitour
https://www.voices.com/profile/emilywahlund

https://www.instagram.com/jupiter.melon.mikey/
